Artist Joe Ng returns to illustrate third arc of Street Fighter Unlimited! While Urien unleashed the strange duo of Necro and Effie to teach a lesson to one nosey fighter, Ryu find himself pitted against a surprise challenger from his past. Plus, Sagat faces Adon in Muay Thai Masters bonus story!

Cover B is part nine of a twelve part connecting cover image made up of all the Ultra Jam Puzzle covers for issues #1-12.The 1:10 Retailer Incentive Homage Cover C is a homage of the cover of Magnus Robot Fighter #1.
